FILES

channels.xml            Python script generating channels list
eggdrop-logger.tcl      Eggdrop 1.8.x script logging IRC
logs.xml                Python script generating logs list

Eggdrop

Install Eggdrop 1.8.x. Currently, Eggdrop 1.8.x can only be installed from the CVS tree. You can obtain a nightly snapshot from the website.

http://www.eggheads.org/

Once installed, place eggdrop-logger.tcl in the eggdrop scripts directory and source it from the configuration file. Be sure to modify the nick to track.

Website

The two files, channels.xml and logs.xml, are python CGI scripts providing XML data. Simply, make them publicly accessible from the web server and call them via JavaScript.
